data.description: This charming 3 bed, 1 bath home is a cozy haven nestled in a prime location. Featuring high vaulted ceilings that give an open feel to this property that is great for first time home buyers or investors. This home is conveniently located near parks, restaurants, shopping, grocery stores, schools and more! With easy quick access to the freeway, this home offers a blend of comfort and accessibility that's hard to beat.
